    <item>
      <title>蒂芙尼因消费下降缩减中国旗舰店规模</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/tiffany-to-halve-china-flagship-store-as-luxury-spending-dives</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，随着奢侈品牌在世界第二大经济体中国的销售额暴跌，路威酩轩集团 (LVMH) 领先的珠宝制造商蒂芙尼 (Tiffany &amp; Co.) 正计划缩小其位于上海的一家面积逾 12,000 平方英尺的旗舰店的规模。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/tiffany-to-halve-china-flagship-store-as-luxury-spending-dives</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 05:00:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾通胀降温至目标水平，利好降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/philippine-inflation-cools-below-estimate-in-boon-for-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾8月份通胀率降至七个月以来的最低水平，并回到央行的目标水平，增加了决策者维持降息周期的空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/philippine-inflation-cools-below-estimate-in-boon-for-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 01:36:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
