    <item>
      <title>爱马仕的成功让远房亲戚的 Z 世代孩子成为百万富翁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/hermes-success-makes-distant-relative-s-gen-z-kids-millionaires</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱马仕国际集团 (Hermès International SCA) 是欧洲最富有的家族，其背后的家族积累了如此巨大的财富，甚至一个远房血亲只需捐赠几股该奢侈品巨头的股票，就能让自己的孩子成为百万富翁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-04/hermes-success-makes-distant-relative-s-gen-z-kids-millionaires</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 08:27:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
